    <h1 class="display-4 text text-center">Welcome to Gift Connect!</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">This is your one stop shop to keep track of all your gift needs.</p>
    <p class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-end">
      <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg justify-content-md-end" id="btn-login" href="login.ejs" role="button">Log
        in</a>
    </p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p>Have you ever been worried that you'll forget to buy a gift for someone? Clear your head by putting those thoughts on your Gift List Connect. One of the most important reasons you should use a to do list, even for gift buying, is that it will help you stay organized. When you write all your tasks in a list, they become more manageable. </p>
    <br>
    <p>What is a Gift List Connect? The definition is a simple one. It's a list of gifts you need to purchase, or gifts that you want receive (under developement). </p>
    <p></p>
